item.title: 508 Running HELP!
item.dc:creator: @rofllewisrofl rofllewisrofl
item.description:
@rofllewisrofl wrote:

A 508 running Error could be caused by several Problems.

  1. Is you’re Cache in the right Place?

  2. Did you Edit the Batch file’s and make sure you have the right JDK Version?

  3. Does you’re computer have enough RAM Too run the server?
